Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:29.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听不见的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸不到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你..你..
